metadata.name: Christmas Ninja Golden Ticket #1
metadata.description: Your special access to the world of the Christmas Ninja. The Golden Ticket unlocks future features and benefits for Christmas Ninja holders as well as being you premium ticket to a treasure chest of prizes. Every 100 Golden Tickets minted will have ten winners drawn for prizes such as: Christmas Ninja Genesis Collection NFTs and free mints in the main Christmas Ninja collection. Plus, hold on to your Golden Ticket for monthly prize draws
